#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_timer.html.heex:36
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
". Timer commands run in the window that was active when the timer was "
"created and do not switch your current window when they fire. Creating a "
"timer with the same name as an existing one replaces the old timer."
msgstr ""
"जब टाइमर बनाया गया था और जब वे आग में अपने वर्तमान विंडो को स्विच नहीं करते "
